CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 9, 1964, pg. 1 reads:" World-Wide Delegation - The nearly 900 delegates attending the Methodist General Conference in Pittsburgh is world-wide, representing many races that inhabit the globe. The Courier cameraman captured some of these in above pictures...-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: 1964 United Methodist Church General Conference, with delegates seated in the audience and stage, with cross, candles and flowers, Civic Arena, another version
